    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Since 1.7 (I think)    when creating form element and setting value 0      it will pass the notEmpty and required=&gt;true validator. 0 is now considered valid value.
Now one should enter empty string instead.
I am not 100% if this is all 1.7 issue but on 1.6.2      '0' was not valid with above validators.</p>

